# School History and Ownership

## Background
This school was established to address the need for quality basic education
within the community, with a strong emphasis on academic excellence and character development.

## Ownership
The school is privately owned and managed under the leadership of the Proprietor,
in line with national education regulations and best practices.

## Governance
Overall policy direction is provided by the Proprietor, supported by the Headteacher
and academic leadership team.
